#

Lemon Garlic Shrimp Bisque with a Touch of Saffron and Chive Oil

$18.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

SeafoodSoupElegantComfort Food

Description

A luxurious, creamy bisque infused with lemon, garlic, and delicate saffron, garnished with vibrant chive oil for a refined touch.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Shallots (finely chopped): 1 medium
  • Garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • Lemon Juice: 1/4 cup
  • Fish Stock: 4 cups
  • Heavy Cream: 1 cup
  • Saffron Threads: 1/4 tsp
  • Chives (finely chopped): 1/4 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
